                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The shadow hit a living creature with a shadow hand Strike on its previous action.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The shadow pulls at the target's shadow, making the creature @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 1} (or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 2} on a critical hit). This is cumulative with other enfeebled conditions from shadows, to a maximum of enfeebled 4. If this increases a creature's enfeebled value to 3 or more, the target's shadow is separated from its body. Enfeebled from Steal Shadow decreases by 1 every hour.</p>"
